<p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px;">2024年6月26日下午，我校第三次校庆工作推进会在行政中心一楼会议室举行。校党委副书记、执行校长范红铭，常务副校长李旺根，以及学校各职能部门负责人、二级学院党总支书记等参加了会议，会议由校友办主任夏光辉主持。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 0em; text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="/data/upload/img/20240705/1720190698803082038.jpg" title="1720190698803082038.jpg" alt="1720190698803082038.jpg" width="600" height="467" border="0" vspace="0" style="width: 600px; height: 467px;"/></span></p><p style="text-indent: 0em;"><span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></span></p><p style="text-indent: 0em;"><span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">会上，<span style="letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: red;">夏光辉首先对前两次校庆工作推进会的情况进行了简要回顾。</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: center; text-indent: 2.21428em; caret-color: red; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">各职能部门负责人和二级学院党总支书记依次详细汇报了所负责的校庆工作任务的推进状况。校庆活动策划安排逐步完善，校友联络与邀请工作有序开展，宣传工作全面铺开，校园环境优化工作稳步推进，文艺表演筹备工作紧锣密鼓。</span><span style="font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-indent: 2.21428em; caret-color: red; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style="text-indent: 0em; text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="/data/upload/img/20240705/1720190790290053542.jpg" title="1720190790290053542.jpg" alt="1720190790290053542.jpg" width="600" height="450" border="0" vspace="0" style="width: 600px; height: 450px;"/></span><br/></p><p style="text-indent: 0em;"><span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span></p><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">常务副校长李旺根也就校庆工作提出具体要求。他指出，要强化部门间的沟通与协作，凝聚强大工作合力，切实提升工作效率。在筹备进程中，严格遵循时间节点，力保各项工作按时、高质完成。</span></section><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2.21428em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">校党委副书记、执行校长范红铭认真聆听汇报后发表重要讲话。他强调，校庆是学校发展的重要里程碑，是彰显学校历史与成就、凝聚师生和校友力量、推动学校未来发展的关键契机。全体人员务必高度重视，精细筹备，务必确保校庆活动顺利圆满。同时，要注重挖掘特色，展现亮点，抓住细节，全方位呈现学校的办学佳绩和独特风貌。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2.21428em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: red; letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">通过本次推进会，明确了校庆工作的目标和任务，进一步凝聚了各方力量，为校庆工作的顺利开展奠定了坚实基础。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 0em;"><span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></span><br/></p>